id":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"Tracking apps係唔係雙方都唔準用？"},{"pid":"67271c6ebe6bf5b2f06d98650d432fe84c4d9753","tid":1643074,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"點解speed cam app唔落架"},{"pid":"62bbdb3c99be04a456170e388b4c11dad47d2a54","tid":1643074,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"支那真係幫大家回好多血"},{"pid":"9e5e589be6f34380e92788417ca7752d41f348ad","tid":1643074,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:00:38.000Z","msg":"本港示威行動持續，早前遭內地官媒點名批評、可以實時顯示警員及警車身處位置等的手機應用程式「HKmap.live即時地圖」，據報已被蘋果公司(Apple)從應用商店中下架。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》引用App Store聲明報道，指「HKmap.live即時地圖」被香港示威者用來追蹤警察行動，相關應用程式會危及執法。聲明提到，蘋果App Store已與香港網絡安全及科技罪案調查科核實，該應用程式已被用於瞄準（target）和伏擊（ambush）香港警察，威脅公共安全。蘋果認為，該APP應用違反了公司準則和香港法律，故從App Store中刪除。<br />\n<br />\n「HKmap.live即時地圖」，可實時顯示警員及警車身處位置、何處施放了催淚彈等。此前，「HKmap.live即時地圖」曾遭蘋果以會鼓勵進行違法活動為由拒絕上架申請，開發者其後上訴，Apple最終批准。"},{"pid":"477520d94fccdc079a0b34f44aff663c74ef8b85","tid":1643074,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445304d510530c5aaa1f34d5b7bcfaa57fd31784","tid":1643074,"uid":60057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e980b39a55bcf21ef87141de52091c8d380acf2b","tid":1643074,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"蘋果係貿易戰撐中?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"蘋果不嬲奶中，呢鑊最主要係睇侵會唔會迫所以美資歸邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279a6c53c926895dc4f07c19a629b871eb80b712","tid":1643074,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zf6QcZL.png\" data